<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MedLink</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="images/iconhead.jpg" />
    <link href="images/logo.jpg" rel="icon" />
    <link href="styles/Aboutus.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.2.0/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-xh6O/CkQoPOWDdYTDqeRdPCVd1SpvCA9XXcUnZS2FmJNp1coAFzvtCN9BmamE+4aHK8yyUHUSCcJHgXloTyT2A=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />

    <link
      href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('includes/header') %>
    <section class="about-us">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <% if (req.session.user) { %>
        <p>
          Welcome back, <%= req.session.user.name %>! Thanks for trusting
          MedLink.
        </p>
        <% } else { %>
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>MedLink</strong>, your trusted partner in finding
          the best healthcare professionals and hospitals near you...
        </p>
        <% } %>

        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          To revolutionize the healthcare experience by connecting patients with
          highly-qualified doctors and hospitals, enabling them to make informed
          decisions and receive the best care possible.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Search for Top Hospitals and Doctors:</strong> Our
            comprehensive database helps you find trusted healthcare providers
            based on your location, medical specialty, and patient reviews.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Doctor Appointments:</strong> Booking an appointment has
            never been easier. Choose your preferred doctor and schedule a visit
            online in just a few simple steps.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Location-Based Search:</strong> Whether you’re at home,
            traveling, or on vacation, we make it easy to locate the best
            healthcare providers in your current area.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Trusted Reviews and Ratings:</strong> We provide honest
            feedback from real patients to help you make informed decisions
            about your healthcare.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose MedLink?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Convenience:</strong> Search and book appointments from
            anywhere, at any time.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Comprehensive Database:</strong> A wide variety of hospitals
            and doctors across different specialties.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Personalized Experience:</strong> Tailored recommendations
            based on your location and medical needs.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Trustworthy:</strong> Our platform ensures you connect with
            reputable healthcare professionals and facilities.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          At <strong>MedLink</strong>, we are committed to your health and
          well-being. Whether you're seeking a routine check-up or specialized
          treatment, our goal is to help you get the care you need, when you
          need it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for choosing <strong>MedLink</strong> — Your Health, Our
          Priority.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="appointment-hospital">
      <div class="section-container">
        <div class="appointment-section">
          <img
            src="images/appointmentbooking.avif"
            alt="Appointment Image"
            class="section-img"
          />
          <div class="text-container">
            <h2>Book an Appointment</h2>
            <p>
              Find the best doctors and schedule your appointment easily through
              our platform. We make booking healthcare appointments hassle-free!
            </p>
            <a href="/Appointment" class="btn">Book Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hospital-section">
          <div class="text-container">
            <h2>Top Hospitals</h2>
            <p>
              Search through a wide range of trusted hospitals near you. Whether
              it's for routine checkups or emergencies, we connect you to the
              right facility.
            </p>
            <a href="/findhospital" class="btn">Explore Hospitals</a>
          </div>
          <img
            src="images/hospital.avif"
            alt="Hospital Image"
            class="section-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="appointment-hospital">
      <div class="section-container">
        <div class="appointment-section">
          <img src="images/doctor.png" alt="Doctor Image" class="section-img" />
          <div class="text-container">
            <h2>Top Doctors</h2>
            <p>
              Search through a wide range of trusted doctors. Either for
              surgeries or checkups. Find the best doctors and schedule your
              appointment easily.
            </p>
            <a href="/finddoctor" class="btn">Book Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hospital-section">
          <div class="text-container">
            <h2>Location Service</h2>
            <p>Search for Healthcare Providers Near You.</p>
            <a href="/findhospital" class="btn">Explore</a>
          </div>
          <img
            src="images/location.avif"
            alt="Hospital Image"
            class="section-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('includes/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
